post_text:
Good evening , this message is for our booster club members.

We will be having our annual meeting this coming Wednesday night at
7:00 pm in the high school gym lobby.

We will be following CDC guidelines and school district Covid 19 requirements so please bring a mask or some sort of face covering.

We would like to see as many of you attend as possible. Have a good evening!
